  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed third floor unit, by reason of its single aspect nature, inadequate floor area and internal head height and lack of private amenity space, would result in an unacceptable standard of accommodation for future occupiers contrary to policies D6 (Housing quality and standards) of The London Plan (2021), policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP17 (Housing Design) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033 (2020); and the guidance contained with the Housing SPG (2016).",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;The proposed development, in the absence of a legal agreement to secure car-free housing, would be likely to promote the use of non-sustainable modes of transport and contribute to air pollution and congestion in the surrounding area, contrary to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;policy T6 (Car Parking) of the London Plan (2021) and policy LP45 (Parking and Car Free Development) of Hackney’s Local Plan 2033 (2020) and Hackney&#x27;s S106 Planning Contributions SPD (2020).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, in the absence of a legal agreement to secure a contribution towards affordable housing fails to deliver the maximum reasonable amount of affordable housing and is therefore contrary to policy H4 (Delivering affordable housing) of the London Plan (2021), policy LP13 (Affordable housing) of Hackney’s Local Plan 2033 (2020) and Hackney&#x27;s S106 Planning Contributions SPD (2020).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "The proposal, by reason of inadequate cycle provision for the top floor unit would fail to adequately provide for sustainable transport contrary to policy LP42 (Walking and cycling) of Hackney Local Plan 2033 (2020) and policy T5 of the London Plan (2021)"
  ],
